# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Nur al-Hadith — Environment Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your keys.
#   cp .env.example .env.local
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Speech Practice ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 🆓 DEFAULT: Local Whisper (Xenova/whisper-small) via Transformers.js
#    Completely free — no API keys needed, no credits, no spending.
#    First load downloads the model (~1.5GB), subsequent loads are instant.
#
#    No env vars required — just start using the speech practice page!
#
# ── OPTIONAL: If you want to use a cloud API instead ─────────────────────
#
# الخيار 1: NVIDIA FastConformer CTC Hybrid Large
# (أفضل نموذج تعرف على الصوت بالعربية — لكن يتطلب دفع)
# https://ngc.nvidia.com
# NVIDIA_API_KEY=nvapi-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#
# الخيار 2: OpenAI Whisper (يدفع، يعطون رصيد مجاني عند التسجيل)
# https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-key-here
#
# ── Optional: Next.js settings ───────────────────────────────────────────
# NODE_ENV=production
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://nur-al-hadith.example.com
